<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Interested in a degree in chemistry, but don’t have the room in your study plan to complete a double-major? Consider pursuing the Chemistry minor. It’s relatively easy, especially if you have passed many of the lower division preparatory courses such as general chemistry, mathematics, and physics.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
